{"word":"G4155 - πνίγω - pnígō - pnee'-go - Choke","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πνίγω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pnígō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pnee'-go</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Choke</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தொண்டையை நெரி, அமிழ்"},{"paragraph":"1. to choke, strangle"},{"paragraph":"2. to wring one's neck, throttle"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Strengthened from <a href=\"#/G4154 - πνέω - pnéō - pneh'-o/4154\">G4154</a>; to <i>wheeze</i>, that is, (causative by implication) to <i>throttle</i> or <i>strangle</i> (<i>drown</i>): - choke, take by the throat.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4155/4155\">G4155</a>, <a href=\"#/G4156/4156\">G4156</a>, <a href=\"#/G4846/4846\">G4846</a>, <a href=\"#/G638/638\">G638</a>"}]}